<p>Hi! I am a Ph.D. student at the Technical University of Munich, supervised by Prof. Javier Esparza and Prof. Igor Walukiewicz.</p>

<p>My research interests include parameterized verification, automata theory and well-quasi orders.
You can find more about my research on <a href="https://dblp.org/pid/215/5409.html">dblp</a>.</p>

